  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Card Streamer Simulator is a simulation game that simulates a card broadcasting room anchor to make money by splitting card packs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, you can make money by splitting card packs through customer orders, or you can spend your own money to experience the fun of splitting cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains over 934 cards, divided into 8 rarity levels: N, R, SR, SSR, SP, UR, LR, and CR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Current version includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>God & Monster X</strong> Series Cards (316 cards)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras/14e4cfc5ba2bc72b8b76d1f6d2585c7b.avif?t=1746691294\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras_big/14e4cfc5ba2bc72b8b76d1f6d2585c7b.avif?t=1746691294 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>God & Monster Y</strong> Series Cards (316 cards)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras/2d3742aa23e82c5cf81a25e540214d79.avif?t=1746691294\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras_big/2d3742aa23e82c5cf81a25e540214d79.avif?t=1746691294 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ark 2099</strong> Series Cards (245 cards)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras/b5c00a4c2cbca6007df853f23fc481b0.avif?t=1746691294\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3592240/extras_big/b5c00